The Legacy Group project was founded by former learners in September this year. The group will focus on collaborating with the school in order to source funding and other support measures to improve Mphanama’s image, educational services and results. Registration for the fun run and walk will kick off at 06:00 at Mphanama Secondary School in Mhluzi, with the race starting at 06:30. Entry fees are R80 for adults and R40 for kids. Tickets are already available at Mphanama Secondary School, Sipho’s Water in the Duduza Complex and Sindi’s Kitchen in the HEDC Centre. Entertainment and music will be provided. Food and beverages will also be on sale. For more information, contact 072 466 7006 or 060 781 3054.